{"tid":2100253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍「福特號」航母部署延誤至2023年 專案負責人遭撤職","createTime":"2020-07-09T02:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T06:36:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c5241698123751a1e1e460867378ed90636d166b","tid":2100253,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，魯坦上校因部署時程延長問題遭到美國海軍部助理部長格茨（James Geurts）撤職，未來將調任海上系統司令部（NAVSEA），該職缺將由曾任「聖安東尼奧號」船塢登陸艦（LPD 17）計畫負責人的梅卡夫（Brian Metcalf）上校接手。<br />\n<br />\nNAVSEA發言人表示，「福特號」航艦的備戰對美國海軍來說是「重中之重」，「福特號」在先前的「總會試後整備期」（PSA）過程中進展順利，但隨後在進行「交艦後測試與試俥」（PDT&amp;T）卻費時長達8個月，即使測試期間受武漢肺炎疫情衝擊，但花費時長仍已遠遠超出預期。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n亨利克斯表示，「福特號」的問題主要在於一次採用過多新技術所致，新技術多達23項，包括對於武裝、彈射系統及回收艦上軍機的系統皆已重新設計。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n然而，福特號已成為美國海軍有史以來最貴的採購案，美國國會一份報告顯示，「福特號」原本在2018年就要部署，現在卻可能要等到2023年，光是福特號一艘航空母艦就花費高達133億美元（約新台幣3951億元）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3222618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3222618&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmtqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=5c4fdd6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3222618&h=3c9e8222\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3222618</a>"},{"pid":"eef080b6954bf0570975ed26746e89782d2d0dad","tid":2100253,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>，光是福特號一艘航空母艦就花費高達133億美元</blockquote>咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d472eb118f54c1f610c0ecf1625a87e1c4f4bc","tid":2100253,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eef080b6954bf0570975ed26746e89782d2d0dad","tid":2100253,"uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>，光是福特號一艘航空母艦就花費高達133億美元</blockquote>咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"由於所費甚鉅，加上戰備考量，前任美國海軍代理部長莫德利亦曾指出：「這條船再貴，美國海軍即使含著淚也得把『她』完工。」"},{"pid":"b77ec3c6c22f4a4f6990eef3810f3531a83d6e93","tid":2100253,"uid":38516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:29:17.000Z","msg":"咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比夠500億美金要求加速部署，順便造多一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c62156a78512efa0d7f74713c6d79b1bade9121","tid":2100253,"uid":183090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:31:29.000Z","msg":"明日大愚個一萬億起個戰鬥群仲有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38c6d07b45bcf327d7742e889e7f8bee5743cc0","tid":2100253,"uid":79892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:39:37.000Z","msg":"美軍爛尾樓都平過高鐵呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a85fe3b11b4acc9703a1a6cd5a2c40b85680eee","tid":2100253,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:41:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd82103c5ba25810cc54d1ba71106d41120755ca","tid":2100253,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3f4ee0fefb4fc2626a38351513a13fe360770f0","tid":2100253,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"美軍爛尾你以為得海軍 空軍都有kc46加油機"},{"pid":"3cbbe1fbca61ba39fb64612766da6b9b37449f6b","tid":2100253,"uid":263944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:45:51.000Z","msg":"香港人見慣一萬億大數字<br />\nfeel唔到100億USD有幾大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"